:53:33.000Z","msg":"條友平時也文也武<br />\n原來係劉德華養嘅狗"},{"pid":"eac80673a686604aa99b315050f328fab01e4874","tid":847622,"uid":43173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"問題唔係佢讚唔讚成填海，係佢係劉德華<br />\n市民身份表達冇問題，公衆人物身份仲要背脊係香港團結基金，立場已經咁鮮明劇本又咁固定，講乜都有問題。"},{"pid":"576134c63c2b5e5e39e6158269494cc953854945","tid":847622,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:21:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">古語2則：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">牛唔飲水唔㩒得牛頭低，<br />\n西唔出水唔屌得西窿入！</span></span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45a73d9eb77d095a28b6e5ca6c0fe59019c29e2","tid":847622,"uid":70423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:32:52.000Z","msg":"其實咪又係藝人要色盲依個問題。 黃子華講過晒啦"},{"pid":"59d339a08f777fdde0d904ef24874235a8877ff0","tid":847622,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6870fbb3f14a1fe9109424a970660915788452f7","tid":847622,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:50:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J8AexA116jY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ8AexA116jY&d=z2mhxptcnXvYxAH54PNQzYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=dbc43198\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J8AexA116jY</a>"},{"pid":"714dd1c1b85b20008b8d7237daf31c78592cb72b","tid":847622,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8be5b2ce709d895df78a71fb1b398f3491ed6347","tid":847622,"uid":27688,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"030726e96beb012c00f3ee201c6d95da4688bb98","tid":847622,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-